OL,3,CFootball fan jailed for one-punch
OL,4,Ckilling of rival supporter
OL,6,FA man who killed a rival football fan
OL,7,Fwith one punch has been jailed.
OL,9,FTony Johnson, who was 55, was among a
OL,10,Fgroup of Blackpool supporters who
OL,11,Fgathered outside the Manchester Pub on
OL,12,Fthe Promenade following the
OL,13,FChampionship tie with Burnley on
OL,14,FMarch, 4 2023.
OL,16,FThe pub had been designated for away
OL,17,Ffans but a disturbance developed
OL,18,Fbetween the rival groups, amongst the
OL,19,Fvisiting fans was Jake Balmforth.
