OL,3,CFootball fan jailed for one-punch
OL,4,Ckilling of rival supporter
OL,6,FHe was caught on CCTV punching Mr
OL,7,FJohnson once in the face, and he
OL,8,Fsuffered a serious head injury.
OL,10,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,11,Fservices at the scene, and care given
OL,12,Fby medical staff at Blackpool Victoria
OL,13,FHospital, he died two days later
OL,14,Fwithout regaining consciousness.
OL,16,FBalmforth, 35, of Tarvin Close,
OL,17,FBurnley, was found guilty of
OL,18,Fmanslaughter by a jury at Preston
OL,19,FCrown Court after a six-day trial
OL,20,Fearlier this month.
