OL,6,FJudge Robert Altham, the Honorary
OL,7,FRecorder of Preston, jailed him for
OL,8,Ffive years at the same court on
OL,9,FThursday.
OL,11,FBalmforth was also given a nine-year
OL,12,Forder banning him from football
OL,13,Fgrounds.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Andy Fallows
OL,16,Fof Lancashire Constabulary's Major
OL,17,FInvestigation Team said: "My thoughts
OL,18,Fremain very much with Tony Johnson's
OL,19,Ffamily.
