OL,3,CFootball fan jailed for one-punch
OL,4,Ckilling of rival supporter
OL,6,F"It has been a harrowing experience
OL,7,Ffor them over the last two years,
OL,8,Flosing a loved one and having to
OL,9,Frelive the events of the evening of 4
OL,10,FMarch 2023 during the trial.
OL,12,F"This case shows how outbreaks of
OL,13,Fviolence can lead to tragedy and what
OL,14,Fthe terrible consequences of one punch
OL,15,Fcan be.
OL,17,F"Jake Balmforth was convicted by the
OL,18,Fjury of Mr Johnson's manslaughter and
OL,19,Fwill have to carry that burden for the
OL,20,Frest of his life."
